HX711 differential amplifier


This module is a differential amplifier designed for measuring data from strain gauges. It has a 24 bit ADC , 2 sets of differential inputs, and up to 128x programmable gain


Connections are.

hx711 <-> Seelab/ExpEYES

VCC - 5V

GND - GND

SCK - OD1

DT - IN2


The load cell is a wheatstone bridge. Use E+, E- and A+ A-


Wire colours may vary depending on where it was purchased.


Tare and conversion to weight units has not been implemented. The scale will vary from cell to cell.
